<section id="servicios" class="py-5" style="background-color: var(--bg-brand);">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="text-center mb-4 font-decorative text-gradient servicios-title">El único hospedaje al nivel del amor que le tienes</h2>
        <p class="text-center mx-auto mb-3 text-muted px-4 px-md-0 lead servicios-lead" style="max-width: 750px; color: var(--primary-color);">Para brindarte una cotización exacta y a la medida es indispensable conocer a tu perrito en persona para evaluar su tamaño y temperamento.</p>

        <!-- Tarjeta de Tarifa de Hospedaje en Verde y Foto -->
        <div class="row align-items-stretch justify-content-between mt-3 g-4 pb-4">
            <!-- Left Side: Pricing Card -->
            <div class="col-lg-5 col-md-5 d-flex flex-column">
                <div class="card h-100 pricing-card">
                    <div class="text-center pt-4 pb-2">
                        <span class="text-muted small fw-bold text-uppercase" style="letter-spacing: 0.1rem;">HOTEL CANINO</span>
                        <h4 class="fw-bold mt-1 mb-0" style="color: var(--primary-color); font-size: 1.4rem;">Hospedaje</h4>
                        <div class="small fw-bold mt-1" style="color: var(--accent-green);">*Promoción de Apertura</div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Ribbon -->
                    <div class="ribbon-wrapper">
                        <div class="pricing-ribbon ribbon-green">
                            <span class="price-period">desde</span>
                            <span class="price-number">$450</span>
                            <span class="price-period">MXN / noche</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="ribbon-fold fold-green"></div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card-body px-4 py-2 d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                        <div>
                            <ul class="list-unstyled text-start mb-4">
                                <li class="mb-3 d-flex align-items-start">
                                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success me-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                                        <path d="M16 8A8 8 0 1 1 0 8a8 8 0 0 1 16 0m-3.97-3.03a.75.75 0 0 0-1.08.022L7.477 9.417 5.384 7.323a.75.75 0 0 0-1.06 1.06L6.97 11.03a.75.75 0 0 0 1.079-.02l3.992-4.99a.75.75 0 0 0-.01-1.05z"></path>
                                    </svg>
                                    <span>Amplias suites individuales climatizadas (sin jaulas)</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="mb-3 d-flex align-items-start">
                                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success me-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                                        <path d="M16 8A8 8 0 1 1 0 8a8 8 0 0 1 16 0m-3.97-3.03a.75.75 0 0 0-1.08.022L7.477 9.417 5.384 7.323a.75.75 0 0 0-1.06 1.06L6.97 11.03a.75.75 0 0 0 1.079-.02l3.992-4.99a.75.75 0 0 0-.01-1.05z"></path>
                                    </svg>
                                    <span>Opción de cuartos para miembros adicionales de la familia</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="mb-3 d-flex align-items-start">
                                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success me-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                                        <path d="M16 8A8 8 0 1 1 0 8a8 8 0 0 1 16 0m-3.97-3.03a.75.75 0 0 0-1.08.022L7.477 9.417 5.384 7.323a.75.75 0 0 0-1.06 1.06L6.97 11.03a.75.75 0 0 0 1.079-.02l3.992-4.99a.75.75 0 0 0-.01-1.05z"></path>
                                    </svg>
                                    <span>Actividades de enriquecimiento y socialización diaria</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="mb-3 d-flex align-items-start">
                                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success me-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                                        <path d="M16 8A8 8 0 1 1 0 8a8 8 0 0 1 16 0m-3.97-3.03a.75.75 0 0 0-1.08.022L7.477 9.417 5.384 7.323a.75.75 0 0 0-1.06 1.06L6.97 11.03a.75.75 0 0 0 1.079-.02l3.992-4.99a.75.75 0 0 0-.01-1.05z"></path>
                                    </svg>
                                    <span>Supervisión profesional 24/7</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="mb-3 d-flex align-items-start">
                                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success me-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                                        <path d="M16 8A8 8 0 1 1 0 8a8 8 0 0 1 16 0m-3.97-3.03a.75.75 0 0 0-1.08.022L7.477 9.417 5.384 7.323a.75.75 0 0 0-1.06 1.06L6.97 11.03a.75.75 0 0 0 1.079-.02l3.992-4.99a.75.75 0 0 0-.01-1.05z"></path>
                                    </svg>
                                    <span>Reportes diarios</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="mb-3 d-flex align-items-start">
                                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success me-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                                        <path d="M16 8A8 8 0 1 1 0 8a8 8 0 0 1 16 0m-3.97-3.03a.75.75 0 0 0-1.08.022L7.477 9.417 5.384 7.323a.75.75 0 0 0-1.06 1.06L6.97 11.03a.75.75 0 0 0 1.079-.02l3.992-4.99a.75.75 0 0 0-.01-1.05z"></path>
                                    </svg>
                                    <span>Webcam áreas comunes</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="mb-3 d-flex align-items-start">
                                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success me-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                                        <path d="M16 8A8 8 0 1 1 0 8a8 8 0 0 1 16 0m-3.97-3.03a.75.75 0 0 0-1.08.022L7.477 9.417 5.384 7.323a.75.75 0 0 0-1.06 1.06L6.97 11.03a.75.75 0 0 0 1.079-.02l3.992-4.99a.75.75 0 0 0-.01-1.05z"></path>
                                    </svg>
                                    <span>Webcam habitación individual (opcional)</span>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-center pt-2 pb-3">
                            <a href="#booking" class="btn btn-pricing-green rounded-pill px-4 py-2 fw-bold w-100">Quiero reservar</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Right Side: Photo -->
            <div class="col-lg-5 col-md-5 d-flex flex-column">
                <img src="/assets/img/perro_maleta.webp" alt="Perro feliz descansando en Bark & Co." class="img-fluid rounded-4 shadow-lg w-100" style="object-fit: cover; aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    @media (max-width: 991px) {
        .servicios-lead {
            font-size: 1rem !important;
            line-height: 1.6 !important;
        }
    }

    .servicios-title {
        font-size: 2.4rem;
    }
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .servicios-title {
            font-size: 3.2rem;
        }
    }
    @media (min-width: 992px) {
        .servicios-title {
            font-size: 3.8rem;
        }
    }

    .pricing-card {
        position: relative;
        margin-left: 21px;
        background-color: var(--white);
        border: 1px solid rgba(156, 132, 94, 0.15) !important;
        border-radius: 1.5rem;
        overflow: visible !important; /* Requerido para dejar salir el listón 3D */
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
        transition:
            transform 0.3s ease,
            box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    @media (max-width: 767px) {
        .pricing-card {
            margin-right: 21px;
        }
    }

    .pricing-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(156, 132, 94, 0.12);
    }

    .ribbon-wrapper {
        position: relative;
        margin-left: -21px;
        margin-right: 0;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .pricing-ribbon {
        position: relative;
        color: white;
        padding: 12px 20px;
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        display: flex;
        align-items: baseline;
        justify-content: center;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        box-shadow: 2px 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 95% 100%, 0 100%);
    }

    .ribbon-green {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4d967c, #356b57);
    }

    .ribbon-fold {
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        bottom: -10px;
        width: 0;
        height: 0;
        border-right: 10px solid transparent;
        border-left: 10px solid transparent;
        z-index: -1;
    }

    .fold-green {
        border-top: 10px solid #23473a;
    }

    .price-number {
        font-size: 2.2rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        line-height: 1;
        margin: 0 6px;
        font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
    }

    .price-period {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        opacity: 0.9;
        font-weight: 500;
    }

    .btn-pricing-green {
        background-color: #4d967c;
        color: white;
        border: none;
        transition:
            background-color 0.3s ease,
            transform 0.2s ease;
    }
    .btn-pricing-green:hover {
        background-color: #356b57;
        color: white;
        transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
</style>
